texts.text: A Zombie is a common undead hostile mob that comes in many variants.

Husk, zombie-like mobs that spawn in the desert and gives hunger when it attacks
Drowned, mobs that spawn in water or if a zombie drowns
Zombie Villager, zombie-like mobs that sometimes spawn instead of a zombie and also spawn when a zombie kills a villager
Zombified Piglin, common mobs that spawn in the Nether
Zombie Horse, unused horses
Giant, unused passive giant zombie mob
Zoglin, zombified hoglins
Chicken Jockey, a baby zombie riding a chicken
Zombie Head, a head of a zombie

Zombie, a basic melee mob found in most places
Armored Zombie, a zombie with armor and weapon
Baby Zombie, a small and faster variant of zombie
Chicken Jockey baby zombie that spawn riding a chicken
Chicken Jockey Tower A variant of Chicken Jockey that features multiple baby zombies stacked on top of each other
Husk, a desert variant of zombie found only in desert locations
Armored Husk, a husk with armor and weapon
Frozen Zombie a snowy zombie that attacks with snowballs in the Creeping Winter DLC
Armored Frozen Zombie, a frozen zombie with armor and weapon
Jungle Zombie, a mossy zombie that poisons players that can be found in the Jungle Awakens DLC
Armored Jungle Zombie, a jungle zombie with armor and weapon
Drowned, a mob that will appear in Hidden Depths DLC
Armored Drowned, a drowned with armor and weapon
Zombified Piglin, a mob that attacks the player with a sword and has more piglin-like sounds than its base game variant
Zombified Piglin Hunter, a ranged variant of the zombified piglin that shoots at players with a crossbow
Zombified Armored Piglin, an armored version of the zombified piglin that attacks with either a Gold Axe or a Firebrand
Zombified Armored Piglin Hunter, the ranged variant of the zombified armored piglin that uses a crossbow
Zombified Fungus Thrower, a mob that throws poisonous fungus that produces blue poison clouds
Zombified Baby Pig, a pet baby pig which is zombified.
